      "content": "thanks... it's just that the weight of it is becoming too much to even exist under. like, i'm just exhausted from trying to fight the sadness every single day. sometimes i wonder if people would even notice if i just stopped being a burden and let the silence take over completely. if the pain is constant, wouldn't it be more peaceful to just... not be here to feel it?",
